1
00:00:05,372 --> 00:00:07,342
"Berdasarkan kisah 'Tale of On Dal in Chronicles of the Three States'."

2
00:00:07,342 --> 00:00:09,367
"Watak, insiden dan tarikh tidak sepadan dengan fakta bersejarah."

3
00:00:10,713 --> 00:00:11,743
"Episod 18"

4
00:00:11,743 --> 00:00:15,043
Puteri makin melampau di hadapan baginda raja.

5
00:00:15,043 --> 00:00:16,208
Itu melampau?

6
00:00:16,482 --> 00:00:18,052
Ramai yang terkorban...

7
00:00:18,052 --> 00:00:19,712
...kerana kekurangan sokongan.

8
00:00:19,712 --> 00:00:20,852
Kenapa awak cakap perkara mengarut?

9
00:00:20,852 --> 00:00:22,217
Mengarut?

10
00:00:22,622 --> 00:00:25,852
Tuan Yeon! Jaga sikit mulut awak!

11
00:00:25,852 --> 00:00:27,723
Saya habiskan seluruh hidup saya di utara...

12
00:00:27,723 --> 00:00:29,857
...melawan orang gasar dan ribut pasir...

13
00:00:30,192 --> 00:00:32,333
...jadi saya tak mampu jaga percakapan saya.

14
00:00:32,333 --> 00:00:33,432
Apa?

15
00:00:33,432 --> 00:00:34,957
Boleh kamu berdua hentikannya?

16
00:00:35,133 --> 00:00:36,457
Tolong bertenang.

17
00:00:37,972 --> 00:00:39,868
Berani dia?

18
00:00:42,402 --> 00:00:44,513
Raja enggan berjumpa dengan tuan puteri...

19
00:00:44,513 --> 00:00:46,013
...dan ia adalah kebimbangan yang besar.

20
00:00:46,013 --> 00:00:48,377
Puteri berjaya mengalahkan tentera Baekje,...

21
00:00:48,712 --> 00:00:50,478
...jadi sumbangan itu patut diambil kira.

22
00:00:55,922 --> 00:00:57,017
Kak Pyeonggang.

23
00:00:58,652 --> 00:01:00,557
Kakak nak menunjuk-nunjuk sebab kakak menang?

24
00:01:00,763 --> 00:01:01,957
Apa maksud awak?

25
00:01:03,862 --> 00:01:06,898
Saya dengar rakyat Goguryeo menangis air mata kesyukuran.

26
00:01:07,633 --> 00:01:09,402
Puteri membantu raja muda...

27
00:01:09,402 --> 00:01:11,268
...dan mendapat pencapaian hebat dalam peperangan.

28
00:01:12,833 --> 00:01:14,503
Kalau bukan kerana kakak...

29
00:01:14,503 --> 00:01:17,437
...bagaimana adik yang lemah dapat menguruskan tugas-tugas raja?

30
00:01:18,143 --> 00:01:20,068
Bukan itu maksud kakak.

31
00:01:22,913 --> 00:01:24,077
Bukankah?

32
00:01:24,413 --> 00:01:25,947
Itu yang saya dengar.

33
00:01:26,283 --> 00:01:30,152
Kakak cuma sedih kerana kita kehilangan orang baik.

34
00:01:30,152 --> 00:01:32,348
Jadi, semasa mesyuarat...

35
00:01:32,693 --> 00:01:35,887
...di depan semua menteri, kakak memarahi raja?

36
00:01:39,193 --> 00:01:40,958
Kakak ingat saya siapa?

37
00:01:42,732 --> 00:01:44,497
Jawablah, Kak Pyeonggang.

38
00:01:45,633 --> 00:01:47,398
Saya rajakah?

39
00:01:48,602 --> 00:01:50,738
Atau adakah saya adik kakak?

40
00:01:51,173 --> 00:01:52,607
Awak ialah raja.

41
00:01:54,512 --> 00:01:55,607
Awak maksudkannya?

42
00:01:56,512 --> 00:01:57,607
Ya.

43
00:02:01,283 --> 00:02:02,753
Kalau awak teruskan sikap melampau tadi...

44
00:02:02,753 --> 00:02:04,547
...saya akan hukum kakak dengan teruk.

45
00:02:05,092 --> 00:02:07,518
Saya akan rampas gelaran tentera kakak.

46
00:02:08,462 --> 00:02:10,057
Sama ada saya sayang atau benci kakak...

47
00:02:10,863 --> 00:02:12,328
...kakak tetap kakak saya.

48
00:02:15,162 --> 00:02:16,328
Kakak boleh keluar.

49
00:02:30,812 --> 00:02:32,948
Awak tak nak buat apa-apakah?

50
00:02:33,152 --> 00:02:34,918
Adakah kita bertarung untuk dapatkan anugerah?

51
00:02:35,252 --> 00:02:37,252
Adakah kita bertarung untuk dapatkan penghormatan?

52
00:02:37,252 --> 00:02:40,048
Jin. Tuan puteri perlu berehat.

53
00:02:40,293 --> 00:02:41,388
Kita patut pergi.

54
00:02:41,662 --> 00:02:43,388
Lepaskan saya.

55
00:02:43,793 --> 00:02:45,293
Kenapa keadaan boleh jadi begini?

56
00:02:45,293 --> 00:02:46,562
Kita menentang Baekje,...

57
00:02:46,562 --> 00:02:48,733
...dan awak, saya dan Ga Jin...

58
00:02:48,733 --> 00:02:50,898
...kembali selepas hampir kehilangan nyawa kita.

59
00:02:51,073 --> 00:02:53,227
Dan raja melayan kita seperti serangga.

60
00:02:54,143 --> 00:02:55,238
Jin.

61
00:03:01,513 --> 00:03:02,777
Dia raja kita.

62
00:03:03,212 --> 00:03:04,648
Dia adik saya...

63
00:03:04,912 --> 00:03:06,877
...tapi sebelum itu, saya adalah pengikutnya.

64
00:03:07,682 --> 00:03:10,493
Saya mahu awak berhenti bercakap begitu di sekeliling saya.

65
00:03:10,493 --> 00:03:12,548
Betul cakap puteri.

66
00:03:14,062 --> 00:03:15,157
Bertenang.

67
00:03:15,863 --> 00:03:18,027
Rumah baru awak dah siap?

68
00:03:18,532 --> 00:03:21,462
Maaf sebab paksa awak berperang sebaik saja awak berkahwin.

69
00:03:21,462 --> 00:03:23,402
Jangan cakap begitu.

70
00:03:23,402 --> 00:03:25,868
Kalau awak panggil, kami akan datang walaupun pada waktu malam.

71
00:03:26,573 --> 00:03:29,168
- Betul tak, sayang? - Jangan panggil saya sayang.

72
00:03:57,203 --> 00:03:59,398
Saya sendiri yang ukir.

73
00:04:01,002 --> 00:04:02,997
Apa pun, ini bermakna kita di pihak yang sama.

74
00:04:03,273 --> 00:04:04,467
Di pihak yang sama?

75
00:04:05,073 --> 00:04:06,368
Kita di pihak yang sama.

76
00:04:08,983 --> 00:04:10,078
Kita dah berkahwin.

77
00:04:11,113 --> 00:04:13,247
Goguryeo yang awak impikan itu, Ga Jin.

78
00:04:14,083 --> 00:04:15,678
Negara yang ingin awak bina.

79
00:04:17,192 --> 00:04:18,688
Saya juga akan tinggal di sana.

80
00:04:19,793 --> 00:04:20,888
Saya...

81
00:04:21,522 --> 00:04:23,727
...wujud di dunia ini untuk menjadi pedang awak.

82
00:04:33,903 --> 00:04:35,002
Nilainya pasti sangat tinggi.

83
00:04:35,002 --> 00:04:37,473
Ia lebih gemuk berbanding yang tadi.

84
00:04:37,473 --> 00:04:39,512
- Ya. - Buka cepat.

85
00:04:39,512 --> 00:04:40,808
Kita patut cepat.

86
00:04:42,113 --> 00:04:43,777
Awak pegang kuat-kuat.

87
00:04:43,783 --> 00:04:46,078
- Mari kita pergi. - Marilah dan...

88
00:04:49,353 --> 00:04:51,493
Ia terperangkap dalam perangkap seseorang...

89
00:04:51,493 --> 00:04:53,892
- ...dan kami nak lepaskannya. - Ya.

90
00:04:53,892 --> 00:04:55,223
- Betul. - Kita patut pergi.

91
00:04:55,223 --> 00:04:57,432
Beri kepada mak awak.

92
00:04:57,432 --> 00:04:58,963
- Mari. - Pergilah.

93
00:04:58,963 --> 00:05:00,998
- Ada herba di sini? - Tidak.

94
00:05:01,702 --> 00:05:02,797
Aduhai.

95
00:05:03,803 --> 00:05:04,898
Apa ini?

96
00:05:05,132 --> 00:05:08,037
Ini perangkap yang kita korek.

97
00:05:08,603 --> 00:05:09,772
Tak guna.

98
00:05:09,772 --> 00:05:11,843
Tolong saya keluar dari lubang ini.

99
00:05:11,843 --> 00:05:13,713
Tolong saya dulu.

100
00:05:13,713 --> 00:05:14,743
Saya dulu!

101
00:05:14,743 --> 00:05:16,907
- Hei! - Tolak saya!

102
00:05:42,202 --> 00:05:44,413
Apa yang kamu buat?

103
00:05:44,413 --> 00:05:46,407
Kalau tak kita boleh makan daging.

104
00:05:47,512 --> 00:05:49,182
Kamu tak dengarkah?

105
00:05:49,182 --> 00:05:51,252
Apa yang mak nak bebelkan sehingga mak ke sini?

106
00:05:51,252 --> 00:05:52,913
Haiwan itu dah mati.

107
00:05:52,913 --> 00:05:55,582
Makan dagingnya buat kita tak rugi apa-apa.

108
00:05:55,582 --> 00:05:57,287
Tak makan juga tak salah.

109
00:05:57,353 --> 00:05:58,692
Lagi sekali.

110
00:05:58,692 --> 00:06:01,487
Semua yang mak cakap kedengaran macam mak membebel?

111
00:06:05,932 --> 00:06:07,027
Dal.

112
00:06:07,663 --> 00:06:08,758
Si dungu.

113
00:06:09,603 --> 00:06:11,667
Jangan pergi semasa mak sedang bercakap.

114
00:06:26,283 --> 00:06:27,578
Aduhai.

115
00:06:27,853 --> 00:06:30,078
Kamu memang anak yang baik.

116
00:06:30,793 --> 00:06:33,963
Pagi dan malam, selama empat tahun...

117
00:06:33,963 --> 00:06:36,157
...kamu asyik menunduk memandang tanah.

118
00:06:37,832 --> 00:06:39,688
Mak adalah ilusi.

119
00:06:41,403 --> 00:06:43,628
- Apa? - Mak...

120
00:06:44,772 --> 00:06:46,967
...adalah orang palsu yang saya cipta dalam fikiran saya.

121
00:06:57,752 --> 00:06:59,378
Mak sebenar saya...

122
00:07:03,382 --> 00:07:05,093
Kenapa kamu tak habiskan ayat itu?

123
00:07:05,093 --> 00:07:06,717
Kenapa dengan mak kamu?

124
00:07:15,502 --> 00:07:18,372
Kenapa kamu selalu ukir benda itu...

125
00:07:18,372 --> 00:07:20,597
...sedangkan kamu tak nak jual?

126
00:07:20,772 --> 00:07:22,338
Ia buat fikiran saya tenang.

127
00:07:22,803 --> 00:07:26,268
Sebab ia mengingatkan kamu kepada isteri kamu apabila kamu pegang?

128
00:07:27,413 --> 00:07:28,578
Mak.

129
00:07:28,582 --> 00:07:31,347
Beritahu perkara sebenar kepada mak.

130
00:07:31,512 --> 00:07:34,423
Dah bertahun kamu tak jumpa puteri.

131
00:07:34,423 --> 00:07:37,688
Kamu nak sangat pergi ke ibu kota.

132
00:07:37,853 --> 00:07:40,388
- Tidak. - Sudah tentu.

133
00:07:41,793 --> 00:07:42,888
Dal.

134
00:07:43,093 --> 00:07:44,758
Saya kata tak boleh!

135
00:07:47,562 --> 00:07:49,758
Awak bercakap dengan siapa?

136
00:07:50,932 --> 00:07:53,498
Tolonglah. Aduhai.

137
00:07:54,243 --> 00:07:56,367
Saya dah cakap jangan datang ke sini lagi.

138
00:07:56,772 --> 00:07:58,367
Awak cakap begitu, musim luruh yang lepas.

139
00:07:58,512 --> 00:08:01,338
Tapi saya nak periksa setiap musim untuk lihat jika awak hidup.

140
00:08:02,243 --> 00:08:04,847
Sekurang-kurangnya kumpulkan tulang awak kalau harimau makan awak.

141
00:08:06,512 --> 00:08:07,617
Dal.

142
00:08:08,153 --> 00:08:10,222
- Janganlah begini. - Lepaskan.

143
00:08:10,223 --> 00:08:12,917
Awak nak berkemas dan pindah ke tempat lain?

144
00:08:13,493 --> 00:08:15,593
Awak fikir saya kembali untuk bermeditasi?

145
00:08:15,593 --> 00:08:16,688
Saya tahu.

146
00:08:17,392 --> 00:08:19,857
Sebab itulah tuan puteri tak boleh datang melawat.

147
00:08:20,192 --> 00:08:21,432
Kerana takut...

148
00:08:21,432 --> 00:08:23,828
...awak akan bertindak melulu dan ke tempat yang kami tak dapat cari.

149
00:08:24,403 --> 00:08:25,498
Sebab itulah...

150
00:08:26,303 --> 00:08:28,938
...dia suruh saya tengok-tengokkan awak.

151
00:08:30,872 --> 00:08:34,477
Pedang tuan puteri sentiasa basah dengan darah.

152
00:08:34,743 --> 00:08:38,048
Tahun ini sahaja, dia sudah sertai lima peperangan.

153
00:08:38,782 --> 00:08:41,083
Sebab dia ambil berat tentang negara dia.

154
00:08:41,083 --> 00:08:42,548
Si dungu.

155
00:08:43,353 --> 00:08:45,048
Ia disebabkan awak.

156
00:08:45,723 --> 00:08:47,223
Kalau dia ada di istana...

157
00:08:47,223 --> 00:08:49,063
...dia tak boleh berhenti berfikir tentang awak...

158
00:08:49,063 --> 00:08:51,162
...jadi dia tawarkan diri untuk pergi dan bertarung.

159
00:08:51,162 --> 00:08:52,757
Untuk menebus ketiadaan awak.

160
00:08:53,563 --> 00:08:55,158
Itulah yang dia akan buat.

161
00:08:57,833 --> 00:08:58,928
Dal.

162
00:08:59,632 --> 00:09:00,897
Datanglah ke ibu kota.

163
00:09:01,973 --> 00:09:04,038
Jumpa puteri...

164
00:09:04,672 --> 00:09:06,737
...dan berbual dengan dia.

165
00:09:15,323 --> 00:09:16,418
Hei!

166
00:09:28,103 --> 00:09:29,963
Kamu nak biarkan dia pergi begitu saja?

167
00:09:29,963 --> 00:09:31,727
Dia kawan lama kamu.

168
00:09:33,833 --> 00:09:35,668
Ia mengganggu kamu juga, bukan?

169
00:09:36,203 --> 00:09:39,467
Tuan puteri pergi berperang dan dibasahi darah.

170
00:09:39,613 --> 00:09:41,208
Dia ada raja.

171
00:09:42,542 --> 00:09:45,382
Mereka adik-beradik, jadi mereka perlu berbaik.

172
00:09:45,382 --> 00:09:48,517
Kamu rasa 10 orang adik lelaki sama seperti seorang suami?

173
00:09:53,122 --> 00:09:54,217
Mak.

174
00:09:54,993 --> 00:09:56,088
Apa?

175
00:09:57,493 --> 00:09:58,892
Kamu nak mak pergi?

176
00:09:58,892 --> 00:10:00,458
Sebab mak membebel?

177
00:10:03,402 --> 00:10:05,227
Saya dan Ga Jin.

178
00:10:06,833 --> 00:10:08,397
Kami tak boleh berjumpa.

179
00:10:11,243 --> 00:10:12,767
Sama ada saya akan mati...

180
00:10:12,973 --> 00:10:15,178
...atau kemalangan yang menimpa Ga Jin...

181
00:10:19,213 --> 00:10:21,048
...pengakhiran kami adalah berdarah.

182
00:10:26,652 --> 00:10:28,788
Untuk menghalangnya daripada berlaku,...

183
00:10:32,933 --> 00:10:35,428
...saya hidup dalam persembunyian dan ini lebih sakit daripada mati.

184
00:10:35,632 --> 00:10:36,857
Macam mana kalau...

185
00:10:37,433 --> 00:10:39,698
...kamu hidup sebagai pertapa sepanjang hayat kamu...

186
00:10:39,973 --> 00:10:41,272
...dan kemudian mati?

187
00:10:41,272 --> 00:10:43,237
Bukankah itu lebih elok?

188
00:10:45,843 --> 00:10:48,007
Kamu orang yang terhebat di Goguryeo.

189
00:10:48,443 --> 00:10:51,078
Kamu juga orang yang paling dungu.

190
00:11:19,772 --> 00:11:21,208
Apa ini?

191
00:11:21,412 --> 00:11:23,338
Memandangkan kakak bukan lagi pegawai tentera...

192
00:11:23,912 --> 00:11:26,308
...kakak ke perpustakaan untuk meluangkan masa.

193
00:11:26,683 --> 00:11:27,778
Dan?

194
00:11:27,983 --> 00:11:32,048
Kakak teringat sesuatu yang mendiang ayah kita cakap.

195
00:11:33,223 --> 00:11:37,058
Wol Gwang katakan ini kepada ayah pada suatu hari.

196
00:11:38,493 --> 00:11:41,058
Masa saya akan tamat.

197
00:11:41,662 --> 00:11:43,933
Dia kata putera mahkota...

198
00:11:43,933 --> 00:11:47,127
...dan puteri akan memerintah Goguryeo.

199
00:11:47,973 --> 00:11:51,367
Ayah dah fikirkan tentangnya dan dia betul.

200
00:11:51,713 --> 00:11:54,007
Kenapa ayah cakap begitu?

201
00:11:55,142 --> 00:11:56,938
Ayah masih kuat.

202
00:11:57,752 --> 00:11:58,908
Tuan puteri.

203
00:12:00,052 --> 00:12:01,152
Ya, ayah.

204
00:12:01,152 --> 00:12:03,247
Apabila putera mahkota menjadi raja,...

205
00:12:03,782 --> 00:12:07,318
...sokong dia dengan sepenuh hati.

206
00:12:08,022 --> 00:12:09,418
Baiklah.

207
00:12:09,963 --> 00:12:12,987
Ayah tak pernah layan kamu dengan baik dan ayah sentiasa...

208
00:12:13,262 --> 00:12:15,198
...berikan kamu lebih tanggungjawab.

209
00:12:16,662 --> 00:12:17,867
Ayah minta maaf.

210
00:12:18,302 --> 00:12:19,397
Jadi...

211
00:12:21,603 --> 00:12:23,272
...kakak nak saya belajar cara-cara untuk memerintah...

212
00:12:23,272 --> 00:12:25,107
...daripada buku-buku yang kakak pilih untuk saya?

213
00:12:25,272 --> 00:12:27,237
Bukannya kakak tiada pengetahuan...

214
00:12:27,542 --> 00:12:29,578
...tapi buku-buku itu akan bantu kakak memerintah.

215
00:12:32,512 --> 00:12:33,778
Apa salahnya?

216
00:12:35,723 --> 00:12:37,147
Saya akan baca.

217
00:12:39,052 --> 00:12:41,757
Tapi saya perlukan bantuan selain daripada buku.

218
00:12:46,833 --> 00:12:48,963
Komander saya dikatakan berani...

219
00:12:48,963 --> 00:12:50,658
...tapi mereka umpama harimau tanpa gigi.

220
00:12:51,032 --> 00:12:53,967
Mereka berkhidmat sejak zaman ayah, jadi mereka sudah tua.

221
00:12:54,542 --> 00:12:55,637
Betul.

222
00:12:56,372 --> 00:12:58,213
Kakak bertarung dengan baik...

223
00:12:58,213 --> 00:12:59,908
...tapi kakak seorang wanita.

224
00:13:00,473 --> 00:13:04,107
Saya nak jadikan suami kakak sebagai Komander Atasan.

225
00:13:06,953 --> 00:13:08,048
Tuanku.

226
00:13:09,223 --> 00:13:10,552
Dah lama dia tiada di sini.

227
00:13:10,552 --> 00:13:12,517
Sudah tiba masanya dia kembali.

228
00:13:13,522 --> 00:13:15,922
Pergi pujuk dia.

229
00:13:15,922 --> 00:13:17,928
Tiada siapa, termasuk kakak boleh buat dia...

230
00:13:18,733 --> 00:13:20,963
...pegang pedangnya lagi.

231
00:13:20,963 --> 00:13:22,097
Aduhai.

232
00:13:23,363 --> 00:13:27,068
Bukankah kakak dan dia jodoh yang ditentukan di syurga?

233
00:13:29,772 --> 00:13:30,938
Kerana kakak...

234
00:13:32,042 --> 00:13:34,278
...dia menderita selama bertahun-tahun.

235
00:13:36,113 --> 00:13:38,747
Kakak takkan paksa dia bertarung lagi.

236
00:13:38,853 --> 00:13:40,313
Go Geon lari ke Silla,...

